This paper involves the analysis of social media data, which falls under the scope of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves natural language processing and image analysis, which are covered by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), respectively. Additionally, the paper deals with issues related to crime and violence, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SD (Software Engineering).
